      <div xml:id="Aink7-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink7">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> yaṟanaṉi ciṟakka vallatu keṭuka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> yuḷaippū marutattuk kiḷaikkuru kirukkun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟaṉṉūrk </l>
          <l> koṇṭaṉaṉ celka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> “May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
          <l> may dharma much prevail, may what is not get lost”,</l>
          <l> thus wants our mother. We,</l>
          <l> “the man from the village by the cool ghat,</l>
          <l> where herons perch on the branches of the myrobalan trees with plume-like flowers,</l>
          <l> let him go as one who takes me to his village”, thus we want. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
